s%2C%20challenging%20the%20classic%20consulting%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22575607dc-c159-497c-83d1-8d5c108f45bf%5C%22%3EXavier%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xavier.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXavier%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edescribes%20itself%20as%20the%20world's%20first%20AI%20strategy%20consultant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Joao%20Filipe%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Xavier%20and%20a%20former%20McKinsey%20consultant%2C%20the%20Xavier%20AI%20chatbot%20can%20provide%20clear%2C%20actionable%20business%20knowledge%20and%20deliverables%2C%20like%20a%2060-page%20business%20plan%2C%20a%20sales%20presentation%2C%20or%20a%20detailed%20marketing%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFilipe%20said%20Xavier%20AI%20has%20its%20own%20proprietary%20reasoning%20engine%20that%20is%20tailor-made%20for%20business%20use%20cases%20and%20can%20provide%20detailed%20sources%20without%20the%20hallucination%20you%20might%20find%20with%20other%20chatbots.%20He%20said%20Xavier%20can%20provide%20both%20strategy%20recommendations%20and%20actionable%20plans%20for%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B99.9%25%20of%20businesses%20could%20really%20never%20afford%20McKinsey%20or%20any%20of%20the%20MBBs%2C%26quot%3B%20Filipe%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20created%20Xavier%20AI%20so%20that%20anyone%20could%20have%20the%20power%20of%20a%20consulting%20firm%20at%20their%20hands%20when%20they%20need%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXavier%20AI%20just%20launched%2C%20but%20Filipe%20said%20he's%20been%20piloting%20it%20with%20different%20clients%2C%20including%20an%20international%20bank%20using%20it%20to%20research%20potential%20clients%20and%20better%20understand%20their%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c97545db-e4e8-4ab2-80da-e543f339beba%5C%22%3EPerceptis%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlibek%20Dostiyarov%2C%20a%20former%20McKinsey%20consultant%2C%20and%20Yersultan%20Sapar%2C%20a%20former%20engineer%20at%20Apple%2C%20cofounded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperceptis-ai-consulting-startup-cofounders-mckinsey-apple-write-proposals-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPerceptis%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20aims%20to%20help%20smaller%20and%20midsize%20firms%20compete%20with%20bigger%20industry%20players%20by%20using%20AI%20to%20streamline%20some%20of%20the%20more%20tedious%20processes%20in%20consulting%2C%20like%20proposal%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerceptis%20is%20now%20focused%20on%20the%20business%20development%20side%20of%20consulting.%20Its%20AI-powered%20operating%20system%20can%20do%20industry%20research%2C%20identify%20opportunities%20that%20align%20with%20their%20client's%20skillset%20and%20background%2C%20and%20create%20detailed%2C%20custom%20proposals%20that%20the%20client%20can%20use%20to%20win%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDostiyarov%20told%20BI%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20internal%20processes%20completed%20at%20consulting%20firms%20are%20heavy%20with%20manual%20labor%20and%20%26quot%3Blend%20themselves%20almost%20perfectly%20to%20what%20GenAI%20is%20capable%20of%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20Perceptis%20could%20make%20smaller%20firms%2C%20which%20don't%20typically%20have%20internal%20AI%20tools%2C%20more%20competitive%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20told%20BI%20this%20week%20that%20while%20initially%20serving%20boutique%20management%20consultancies%2C%20it's%20now%20quickly%20expanding%20to%20serve%20IT%20services%2C%20system%20integrators%2C%20software%20developers%2C%20financial%20services%2C%20design%20firms%2C%20and%20real%20estate%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerceptis%20had%20raised%20%243.6%20million%20in%20funding%20as%20of%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22441b350f-5cb1-4111-a0a6-f4a9920fd1ae%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESIB%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESIB%20specializes%20in%20helping%20clients%20like%20restaurant%20groups%2C%20hospitals%2C%20