20embedded%20around%20crucial%20operating%20processes%20in%20the%20enterprise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20%26quot%3Bvalue%20add%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20lies%20in%20building%20this%20kind%20of%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20unique%20operational%20AI%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243c15cc7-5cf7-4ea8-a813-7d2750dea66e%5C%22%3EFusion%20Collective%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFusion%20Collective%20is%20an%20IT%20consulting%20firm%20that%20offers%20a%20range%20of%20consulting%20services%20to%20clients%2C%20including%20strategy%20and%20management%20advice%2C%20cloud%20transformation%2C%20and%20AI%20alignment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20was%20founded%20by%20Blake%20Crawford%2C%20who%20worked%20on%20enterprise%20architecture%20at%20MTV%20Networks%20and%20Viacom%2C%20and%20Yvette%20Schmitter%2C%20an%20alum%20of%20Deloitte%2C%20PwC%2C%20and%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20where%20she%20led%20three%20cloud%20migrations%2C%20including%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20company's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmitter%20said%20that%20in%20her%20experience%2C%20clients%20are%20seeking%20AI%20advice%20from%20consulting%20firms%20before%20they're%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20organizations%20who%20are%20running%20at%2099%20miles%20an%20hour%2C%20hiring%20these%20firms%20to%20build%20these%20AI%20strategy%20documents%2C%20165%20pages%20of%20beautiful%20PowerPoints%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20But%20these%20companies%20still%20can't%20%26quot%3Boperationalize%26quot%3B%20AI%2C%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhy%3F%20Because%20the%20basic%20infrastructure%20isn't%20there.%20Any%20type%20of%20vulnerability%20that%20they%20have%20in%20security%2C%20their%20cloud%20infrastructure%2C%20is%20just%20exacerbated%20by%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20clients%20chose%20consultants%20based%20on%20trust%2C%20their%20networks%2C%20and%20existing%20business%20relationships%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20believe%20that%20a%20true%20partner%20is%20one%20who's%20going%20to%20tell%20you%20the%20truth.%20Tell%20it%20like%20it%20is%20even%20if%20it%20hurts%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20Schmitter%20said.%20To%20that%20end%2C%20she%20said%20she%20asks%20clients%20who%20come%20to%20her%20about%20AI%20strategy%20to%20have%20a%20solid%20grasp%20of%20their%20infrastructure%20footprint%2C%20data%20governance%20policies%2C%20and%20security%20before%20they%20accelerate%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bottom%20line%20is%20that%20Fusion%20Collective%20likes%20to%20keep%20its%20advice%20real.%20%26quot%3BIf%20companies%20have%20not%20mastered%20the%20fundamentals%2C%20you're%20not%20ready%20for%20AI%2C%20and%20you're%20not%20ready%20for%20an%20army%20of%20consultants%20to%20come%20in%20to%20do%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmitter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bd4ff9a8-fa1d-4c93-a8b5-6bdbdef3a666%5C%22%3ESlideworks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESlideworks%20isn't%20necessarily%20going%20after%20consulting%20firms'%20business%2C%20though%20it%20focuses%20on%20something%20many%20of%20the%20big%20guys%20are%20known%20for%3A%20making%20powerful%20slides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlideworks%20offers%20what%20it%20calls%20%26quot%3Bhigh-end%26quot%3B%20PowerPoint%20templates%20and%20%26quot%3Btoolkits%26quot%3B%20created%20by%20former%20consultants%20for%20Bain%2C%20BCG%2C%20and%20McKinsey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20work%20as%20a%20consultant%20at%20a%20top-tier%20firm%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20are%20schooled%20every%20day%20in%20best%20practice%20presentations%20and%20slide%20design%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20says%20on%20its%20website.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20offer%20access%20to%20a%20library%20of%20slides%20and%20spreadsheets%20for%20areas%20including%20strategy%2C%20supply%20chain%20management%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20transformation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20February%20blog%20post%2C%20Alexandra%20Hazard%20Kampmann%2C%20a%20Slideworks%20partner%2C%20wrote%20that%20%26quot%3Bmanagement%20consultants%20are%20often%20made%20fun%20of%20as%20'slide%20monkeys.'%26quot%3B%20Yet%2C%20she%20added%2C%20the%20slide%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrucial%20reason%26quot%3B%20why%20McKinsey%20and%20BCG%20consultants%20have%20so%20many%20Fortune%20500%20companies%20as%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlideworks%C2%A0offers%C2%A0a%20%26quot%3Bconsulting%20toolkit%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20contains%20205%20slides%20and%20costs%20%24129.%20It%20also%20offers%20a%20%26quot%3Bconsulting%20proposal%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20242%20slides%20plus%20an%20Excel%20model%20and%20costs%20%24149.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20operations%2C%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions%2C%20business%20strategy%2C%20and%20product%20strategy%20templates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlideworks%20says%20it%20has%20more%20than%204%2C500%20customers%20globally%2C%20including%20Coca-Cola%2C%20Pfizer%2C%20and%20the%20professional-services%20firms%20Deloitte%20and%20EY.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2287c6bace-c1e6-4cab-831a-266143de47fc%5C%22%3EUnity%20Advisory%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20top%20UK%20executives%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalary-of-consultants-accountants-big-4-deloitte-kpmg-ey-pwc-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EErnst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20and%20PwC%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20joining%20forces%20to%20launch%20a%20new%20firm%20called%20Unity%20Advisory%20in%20June%2C%20the%20Financial%20Times%20reported.%20The%20firm%20will%20be%20chaired%20by%20Steve%20Varley%2C%20who%20spent%20nearly%2019%20years%20at%20EY%2C%20and%20led%20by%20CEO%20Marissa%20Thomas%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20PwC%20for%20over%2030%20years%2C%20according%20to%20their%20LinkedIn%20profiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20backed%20by%20up%20to%20%24300%20million%20from%20Warburg%20Pincus%2C%20a%20private%20equity%20firm%2C%20and%20will%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efocus%20on%20tax%20and%20accounting%20services%2C%20technology%20consulting%2C%20and%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%