D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-china-hits-back-125-percent-retaliatory-levy-us-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrade%20war%20with%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20led%20to%20a%20staggering%20125%25%20tariff%20on%20goods%20from%20one%20of%20America's%20biggest%20trading%20partners.%20Most%20countries%20worldwide%20were%20%E2%80%94%20and%20may%20still%20be%2C%20come%20July%20%E2%80%94%20subject%20to%20what%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20called%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%26quot%3B%20tariffs%2C%20which%20were%20calculated%20using%20a%20convoluted%20formula%20that%20sought%20to%20correct%20trade%20deficits.%20And%20Trump%20laid%20into%20Jerome%20Powell%20with%20his%20usual%20disregard%20for%20diplomatic%20tact%2C%20calling%20the%20Fed%20chair%20%26quot%3Ba%20major%20loser%26quot%3B%20and%20floating%20the%20possibility%20of%20firing%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Trump's%20tough%20talk%2C%20however%2C%20things%20could%20increasingly%20be%20heading%20toward%20a%20reality%20that%20resembles%20something%20normal.%20That's%20because%20it%20appears%20the%20bond%20market%20has%20defanged%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20two%20occasions%20now%20%E2%80%94%20once%20on%20April%209%20and%20again%20on%20April%2022%20%E2%80%94%20Trump%20has%20backed%20down%20from%20aggressive%20tariff%20proposals%20and%20suggestions%20that%20he%20could%20replace%20Fed%20leadership%20when%20Treasury%20yields%20have%20jumped%2C%20a%20signal%20that%20investors%20could%20be%20losing%20confidence%20in%20the%20US.%20Investors%20arguably%20don't%20have%20to%20pay%20as%20close%20attention%20to%20Trump's%20every%20word%20on%20trade%20and%20the%20Fed%20now%20that%20they%20can%20seemingly%20count%20on%20a%20Trump%20put%2C%20where%20he%20backs%20off%20extreme%20positions%20to%20assuage%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20saying%20the%20tariff%20headlines%20won't%20still%20move%20markets%2C%20but%20there%20are%20hints%20the%20markets%20are%20starting%20to%20view%20non-political-related%20headlines%20(threats%2C%20random%20thoughts%2C%20impromptu%20answers%20to%20tariff%20questions)%20as%20a%20type%20of%20'white%20noise'%20that%20just%20goes%20on%20in%20the%20background%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tom%20Essaye%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Sevens%20Report%20Research%2C%20in%20a%20note%20earlier%20this%20month.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20that%20continues%2C%20it%20should%20help%20calm%20the%20intraday%20volatility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20investors%20might%20expect%20a%20higher%20degree%20of%20normality%20going%20forward%3F%20Things%20are%20already%20just%20about%20as%20uncertain%20as%20they%20can%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEconomic%20policy%20uncertainty%20%E2%80%94%20a%20gauge%20that%20tracks%20news%20coverage%20of%20economic%20uncertainty%2C%20differences%20among%20forecasters%2C%20and%20more%20%E2%80%94%20in%20March%20hit%20the%20highest%20levels%20since%20May%202020.%20While%20that%20sounds%20foreboding%2C%20history%20shows%20that%20significant%20spikes%20like%20this%20don't%20last%20very%20long%2C%20and%20much%20of%20the%20uncertainty%20may%20already%20be%20priced%20into%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Economic%20Policy%20Uncertainty%20Index%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680bc70ea466d2b74ab433fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBaker%2C%20Scott%20R.%2C%20Bloom%2C%20Nick%20and%20Davis%2C%20Stephen%20J.%2C%20Economic%20Policy%20Uncertainty%20Index%20for%20United%20States%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Lefkowitz%2C%20the%20head%20of%20US%20equities%20at%20UBS%20Global%20Wealth%20Management%2C%20said%20in%20a%20client%20note%20on%20Friday%20that%20uncertainty%20topping%20out%20would%20be%20positive%20for%20the%20equity-market%20outlook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20we%20may%20be%20reaching%20peak%20policy%20uncertainty.%20If%20so%2C%20that%20would%20be%20an%20important%20inflection%20point.%20Stocks%20tend%20to%20move%20inversely%20with%20policy%20uncertainty%2C%26quot%3B%20Lefkowitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20uncertainty%20declines%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20key%20tailwind%20for%20stocks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20expect%20equity%20markets%20to%20remain%20choppy%2C%20the%20risk-reward%20for%20stocks%20is%20looking%20more%20appealing%2C%20especially%20now%20that%20we%20know%20that%20Trump%20is%20attuned%20to%20the%20risks%20from%20his%20tariff%20policies.%20We%20maintain%20our%20year-end%202025%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20price%20target%20of%205%2C800.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20there's%20a%20large%20caveat%20to%20a%20potentially%20normalizing%20market%20environment%3A%20the%20possibility%20of%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20hasn't%20reached%20an%20official%20deal%20with%20any%20US%20trading%20partners%20to%20reduce%20his%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20before%20his%2090-day%20deadline.%20No%20agreement%20has%20been%20reached%20with%20China%2C%20either.%20Plus%2C%2010%25%20baseline%20tariffs%20on%20all%20imports%20are%20still%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20uncertainty%20for%20business%20leaders%20and%20the%20concrete%20effects%20of%20tariffs%20on%20profits%2C%20consumer%20prices%2C%20and%20spending%20remain%20to%20be%20seen.%20Many%20economists%20see%20elevated%20recession%20risks%20in%20the%20months%20ahead%2C%20a%20scenario%20that%20likely%20sends%20investors%20fleeing%20from%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20the%20economy%20hangs%20tough%20after%20all%2C%20investors%20could%20soon%20see%20a%20return%20to%20the%20calmer%20seas%20of%20a%20few%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-normal-again-for-investors-tariffs-trade-war-trump-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745827202