gent.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20wrote%20that%20it%20wants%20people%20to%20help%20create%20the%20%26quot%3Bnext%20generation%20of%20intelligent%20product%20experience%26quot%3B%20centered%20on%20large%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECandidates%20are%20expected%20to%20have%20product%20management%20experience%20and%20be%20proficient%20in%20product%20and%20visual%20design%2C%20the%20notice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%20is%20also%20hiring%20a%20chief%20financial%20officer%20and%20chief%20operating%20officer%20%E2%80%94%20jobs%20not%20labeled%20urgent.%20The%20company%20is%20expanding%20its%20research%20and%20engineering%20teams%2C%20according%20to%20other%20listings%20on%20its%20WeChat%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20marks%20a%20major%20shift%20for%20the%20company%2C%20which%20has%20been%20focused%20on%20fundamental%20AI%20model%20research.%20Last%20month%2C%20DeepSeek%20released%20an%20upgraded%20version%20of%20its%20open-source%20V3%20large%20language%20model%2C%20boosting%20its%20reasoning%20and%20coding%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202023%20by%20Chinese%20entrepreneur%20Liang%20Wenfeng%2C%20DeepSeek%20made%20headlines%20and%20disrupted%20markets%20in%20January%20after%20unveiling%20its%20low-cost%20reasoning%20model%2C%20R1.%20The%20startup%20claims%20R1%20can%20rival%20top%20competitors%20like%20OpenAI's%20GPT-4%20%E2%80%94%20but%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-deepseek-integrate-ai-consolidation-us-openai-paywall-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAn%20analyst%20told%20Business%20Insider%20earlier%20this%20month%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20DeepSeek's%20latest%20models%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20the%20reasoning-focused%20R1%20and%20R2%20set%20to%20launch%20later%20this%20month%20or%20in%20May%20%E2%80%94%20mark%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20inflection%20point%26quot%3B%20in%20China's%20AI%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20models%20not%20only%20match%20the%20best-in-class%20performance%20globally%2C%20but%20are%20also%20open-sourced%20under%20the%20most%20permissive%20MIT%20License%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wei%20Sun%2C%20the%20principal%20analyst%20for%20AI%20at%20Counterpoint%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20changes%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20flagship%20models%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20are%20typically%20closed-sourced%20and%20monetized%20through%20APIs%20or%20enterprise%20licensing%2C%20DeepSeek's%20models%20like%20R1%20and%20V3%20are%20free%20for%20anyone%20to%20download%2C%20modify%2C%20and%20integrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%20has%20been%20quiet%20about%20the%20progress%20of%20its%20next-generation%20R2%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20high%20costs%20and%20chip%20shortages%2C%20Chinese%20firms%20have%20been%20prioritizing%20AI%20integration%20and%20consolidation%20to%20stay%20competitive%2C%20an%20analyst%20told%20BI%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETencent%20has%20deployed%20its%20Hunyuan%20model%20and%20DeepSeek%20R1%20across%20its%20massive%20ecosystem%2C%20including%20WeChat%2C%20said%20Ray%20Wang%2C%20a%20Washington-based%20analyst%20who%20specializes%20in%20AI%20and%20US-China%20tech%20statecraft.%20WeChat%2C%20China's%20biggest%20social%20media%20app%2C%20is%20used%20by%20nearly%201.4%20billion%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaidu%20has%20also%20integrated%20DeepSeek%20R1%20into%20its%20search%20engine%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20details%20about%20DeepSeek's%20hiring%20process%20are%20scant%2C%20Liang%2C%20the%20founder%2C%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepseek-founder-liang-wenfeng-hiring-inexperienced-candidates-china-ai-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20values%20creativity%20over%20experience%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20hiring%3C%2F