.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20why%20I%20think%20people%20should%20think%20twice%20before%20buying%20from%20these%20TikTokers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226fd91773-8fc1-42da-98a0-b863052a1170%5C%22%3EHerm%C3%A8s%3F%20Think%20again.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20common%20knowledge%20that%20some%20brands%20make%20their%20products%20in%20China%20%E2%80%94%20no%20one's%20surprised%20by%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20Chinese%20TikTokers%20have%20gone%20further%20and%20claimed%20they%20make%20the%20high-end%20goods%20that%20luxury%20brands%20just%20slap%20their%20labels%20onto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20not%20true.%20Herm%C3%A8s%2C%20for%20one%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F04%2F24%2Ftechnology%2Fchinese-factories-tiktok-trade-war.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520spokesman%2520for%2520Hermes%2520said%2Cproduction%2520costs%2520from%2520a%2520factory.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclapped%20back%20at%20these%20claims.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHerm%C3%A8s%20has%20invested%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20in%20ateliers%20in%20France%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20Europe.%20The%20brand's%20items%20are%20also%20handmade%20by%20trained%20craftspeople.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20scroll%20on%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram%20and%20think%20that%20if%20something's%20been%20put%20online%2C%20it%20must%20be%20real.%20Don't%20believe%20everything%20you%20see%20on%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f60a58a1-3709-437d-b6d7-68d51955fc23%5C%22%3EDon't%20expect%20comparable%20quality%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20look%20at%20these%20Chinese%20versions%20of%20these%20bags%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20where%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftelltale-signs-of-fake-luxury-handbag-from-vintage-luxury-expert-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20expertise%3C%2Fa%3E%20comes%20in%20%E2%80%94%20I%20can%20tell%20the%20Chinese%20TikTokers'%20versions%20are%20fake%20at%20a%20glance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20handles%20are%20the%20wrong%20shape%2C%20and%20the%20proportions%20are%20off.%20The%20handles%20of%20fake%20bags%20are%20often%20a%20dead%20giveaway.%20They're%20either%20too%20tall%20or%20too%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20bags%20in%20the%20videos%20are%20way%20too%20wide%20at%20the%20bottom%2C%20and%20some%20are%20too%20narrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20a%20video%20where%20a%20girl%20was%20holding%20up%20what%20she%20said%20was%20a%20mini%20Kelly%2C%20saying%20she%20got%20it%20directly%20from%20the%20brand's%20manufacturer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20fake.%20It%20didn't%20even%20have%20the%20right%20handle%E2%80%94a%20flat%20handle%20instead%20of%20a%20regular%20rolled%20handle%2C%20which%20immediately%20raised%20a%20major%20red%20flag.%20It%20also%20had%20a%20leather%20grain%20that%20I've%20never%20seen%20on%20a%20Herm%C3%A8s%20bag%20in%20my%20entire%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222c0f7c09-3630-4c3b-b0f1-62a0042a5d04%5C%22%3EWhy%20not%20buy%20resale%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20a%20resale%20or%20a%20new%20authentic%20item%2C%20you%20have%20the%20option%20to%20sell%20it.%20You%20don't%20have%20that%20opportunity%20with%20a%20fake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20advise%20that%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20luxury%20handbag%20at%20a%20marked-down%20price%2C%20buy%20the%20bag%20secondhand%20instead%20of%20from%20people%20who%20claim%20to%20be%20the%20brand's%20Chinese%20manufacturer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECost%20may%20be%20an%20issue%20for%20some%20buyers.%20If%20luxury%20stores%20hike%20prices%20because%20of%20the%20tariffs%2C%20you%20may%20be%20looking%20at%20a%20bag%20that's%20out%20of%20your%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20you%20can%20also%20buy%20bags%20on%20resale%20platforms.%20People%20can%20usually%20find%20popular%20bags%20in%20excellent%20condition%20or%20even%20brand%20new%2C%20and%20prices%20will%20still%20be%20below%20retail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1203492-96bc-40be-a6d5-942fb43bbbb8%5C%22%3EThink%20about%20wh