gy%20startup%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKo%20said%20the%20benefits%20of%20being%20part%20of%20a%20club%20are%20greater%20when%20one%20is%20just%20starting%20out%20and%20has%20little%20internship%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20say%20if%20you%20are%20just%20a%20freshman%2C%20there's%20nothing%20on%20your%20CV%2C%20work%20experience-wise.%20So%2C%20how%20can%20you%20fill%20in%20the%20blank%20page%20as%20soon%20as%20you%20can%3F%20It's%20by%20joining%20these%20kinds%20of%20clubs%20where%20you%20can%20try%20to%20gain%20some%20experience%20and%20have%20them%20as%20bullet%20points%20to%20showcase%20your%20skillsets%2C%26quot%3B%20Ko%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKo%20said%20internships%20remain%20critical%20for%20those%20wanting%20to%20land%20a%20job%20at%20a%20top%20investment%20bank.%20Based%20on%20his%20experience%20coaching%20students%2C%20Ko%20said%20applicants%20will%20need%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20quality%20internship%20experiences%20to%20make%20the%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdrian%20Choo%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20a%20Singapore-based%20career%20strategy%20consultancy%2C%20Career%20Agility%20International%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20employers%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20hire%20members%20who%20participate%20actively%20in%20club%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20just%20an%20ordinary%20member%2C%20that%20would%20help.%20But%20if%20you%20are%20an%20organizer%20or%20an%20executive%20committee%20member%2C%20that%20would%20be%20quite%20impressive%20as%20well%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20have%20organized%20events.%20That%20would%20set%20you%20apart%20from%20the%20rest%2C%26quot%3B%20Choo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20there's%20a%20major%20plus%20point%20of%20being%20part%20of%20a%20club%2C%20said%20Dominic%20Lee%2C%2027%2C%20a%20former%20president%20of%20SMU-SMIF%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20has%20less%20to%20do%20with%20embarking%20on%20the%20golden%20road%20to%20a%20big%20banking%20job%2C%20and%20more%20to%20do%20with%20the%20community%20you%20become%20a%20part%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee%2C%20who%20is%20now%20an%20analyst%20at%20a%20European%20bulge%20bracket%20investment%20bank%2C%20graduated%20from%20SMU%20with%20a%20business%20degree%20in%202023.%20He%20said%20his%20job%20search%20became%20far%20less%20daunting%20because%20he%20had%20friends%20in%20the%20SMU-SMIF%20who%20were%20all%20in%20the%20same%20boat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20running%20a%20marathon.%20Anyone%20can%20run%20a%20marathon%20on%20their%20own%2C%20but%20if%20you%20join%20a%20run%20club%2C%20you%20get%20friends%20to%20train%20with%2C%20advice%20on%20the%20best%20gear%2C%20and%20shared%20training%20plans%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20journey%20is%20just%20a%20lot%20more%20enjoyable%20with%20a%20community%20around%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-college-clubs-where-students-hustle-finance-jobs-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745806645000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67251128a0a0cc14f2258baa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-college-clubs-where-students-hustle-finance-jobs-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Singapore%20Management%20University%20Student%20Managed%20Investment%20Fund%20said%20it%20sees%20over%20200%20applicants%20vying%20for%20around%2020%20spots%20annually.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-college-clubs-where-students-hustle-finance-jobs-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Dark%20Winds%E2%80%99%20Season%203%20Finale%3A%20Unpacking%20the%20Emotional%20Ending%2C%20What%E2%80%99s%20in%20Store%20for%20Joe%20and%20Emm