0out%20of%20law%20school%20to%20focus%20on%20growing%20the%20brand%2C%20now%20available%20in%203%2C000%20stores%20globally.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20are%20five%20pieces%20of%20advice%20he%20would%20give%20to%20anyone%20thinking%20about%20starting%20their%20own%20brand.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Chris%20Hwang%2C%20the%2033-year-old%20cofounder%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thegoldenduck.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Golden%20Duck%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20Singaporean%20snack%20brand.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-golden-duck-singaporean-snack-company-chris-hwang-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChris%20Hwang%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cofounder%20of%20The%20Golden%20Duck.%20At%2023%2C%20I%20dropped%20out%20of%20law%20school%20to%20start%20the%20snack%20brand%2C%20which%2C%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20is%20now%20sold%20in%20over%203%2C000%20stores%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Golden%20Duck%20is%20a%20gourmet%20snack%20brand%20that%20reimagines%20Asian%20flavors%20like%20salted%20egg%20yolk.%20Our%20vision%20has%20always%20been%20to%20be%20the%20Ben%20%26amp%3B%20Jerry's%20of%20snacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20some%20of%20The%20Golden%20Duck's%20snacks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a0777a7bb3f854015b78a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Golden%20Duck%20prides%20itself%20on%20reimagining%20Asian%20flavors%20in%20the%20form%20of%20fun%20snacks.%3Cp%3EThe%20Golden%20Duck%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20small.%20In%202015%2C%20we%20launched%20with%20just%20one%20product%20%E2%80%94%20salted%20egg%20yolk%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%2C%20our%20capacity%20was%20so%20limited%20that%20we%20made%20the%20products%20in%20a%20home%20kitchen.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20could%20only%20make%20about%2050%20packs%20of%20chips%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20started%20getting%20more%20popular%20in%20Singapore%2C%20we%20scaled%20up%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdding%20staff%2C%20maintaining%20quality%2C%20and%20controlling%20the%20processes%20when%20we%20scaled%20up%20were%20some%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20parts%20of%20our%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20also%20weathered%20many%20storms.%20The%20pandemic%20was%20a%20very%20bad%20time%20for%20the%20business%2C%20and%20all%20our%20tourism%20revenue%20evaporated%20overnight.%20We%20had%20to%20reduce%20our%20workforce%20from%20200%20to%20120%2C%20and%20tell%20friends%20we'd%20brought%20on%20board%20that%20we%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20work%20together%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20my%2010%20years%20of%20experience%20running%20The%20Golden%20Duck%2C%20here%20are%20five%20pieces%20of%20advice%20I'd%20give%20to%20anyone%20thinking%20about%20starting%20a%20new%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dff7828b-d187-40dd-9f51-44390bf38a9f%5C%22%3E1.%20Get%20started%20and%20test%20cheap%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20thinking%20about%20it%20and%20you've%20not%20yet%2C%20just%20get%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20have%20to%20quit%20your%20job.%20You%20can%20do%20something%20on%20the%20weekends%2C%20but%20start%20building%20a%20road%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENothing%20is%20stopping%20you%20from%20testing%20it%20right%20now.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20spend%20thousands%20or%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20building%20things%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20dream%2C%20just%20get%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20fail%20at%20first.%20This%20is%20actually%20my%20fifth%20startup%2C%20but%20the%20failures%20gave%20me%20the%20fire%20to