ing%20for%20food%20delivery%20apps%20like%20Uber%20Eats%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20there's%20no%20feeling%20like%20it.%20I%20have%20never%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-make-money-gig-worker-uber-lyft-doordash-delivery-driver-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20so%20much%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20working%20for%20it%2C%20not%20gambling.%20But%20when%20you've%20worked%20on%20a%20Tuesday%20and%20Wednesday%20and%20you%20get%20average%20orders%2C%20Friday%20and%20Saturday%20feels%20like%20a%20cash%20grab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20many%20people%20would%20order%20food%20when%20the%20weekend%20came%2C%20and%20Uber%20needed%20more%20drivers%2C%20so%20pay%20would%20surge.%20You'd%20hear%20that%20%26quot%3Bping%26quot%3B%20sound%20a%20lot%20when%20you%20offered%20an%20order.%20It's%20like%20being%20a%20casino%2C%20you're%20hearing%20it%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20though%2C%20my%20earnings%20started%20falling%2C%20and%20demand%20wasn't%20what%20it%20was%20in%202022.%20One%20day%2C%20I%20took%20a%20ride%20through%20Lyft%20as%20a%20passenger%2C%20and%20the%20driver%20just%20offered%20up%20that%20he%20had%20just%20made%20%24500%20in%20two%20days%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Monday%20and%20Tuesday%2C%20no%20less%2C%20which%20were%20some%20of%20my%20slowest%20days%20as%20a%20delivery%20worker.%20So%20I%20signed%20up%20with%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20as%20a%20rideshare%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Justin%20St.%20James%20faces%20the%20camera%20in%20front%20of%20a%20dark%20window%20wearing%20a%20gray%20t-shirt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680b9962a466d2b74ab42873%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJustin%20St.%20James%3Cp%3EJustin%20St.%20James%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20and%20other%20technology%20companies%20use%20algorithms%20that%20are%20very%20sophisticated.%20There%20are%20parts%20of%20these%20apps%20that%20keep%20us%20hooked%20on%20them%2C%20which%20is%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20running%20a%20business.%20I%20love%20Netflix%2C%20but%20what%20are%20they%20trying%20to%20do%20by%20showing%20you%20another%20episode%20a%20few%20seconds%20after%20the%20last%20one%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20me%2C%20working%20for%20Uber%20felt%20similar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20addictive.%20You%20got%20a%20dopamine%20hit%20when%20the%20app%20offered%20you%20an%20order.%20It%20also%20encouraged%20you%20to%20keep%20working%20with%20surge%20pricing%20and%20heat%20maps%20that%20show%20where%20Uber%20says%20the%20most%20demand%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20as%20drivers%20and%20delivery%20workers%2C%20we%20don't%20always%20get%20information%20from%20Uber%20that%20allows%20us%20to%20make%20critical%20decisions%20about%20whether%20a%20job%20is%20worth%20it.%20I%20wasn't%20always%20able%20to%20see%20exactly%20where%20you're%20picking%20up%20someone%20or%20dropping%20them%20off%20before%20I%20accepted%20a%20ride%2C%20which%20seems%20unbelievable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20night%2C%20I%20picked%20up%20a%20guy%20as%20my%20last%20ride%20of%20the%20night.%20I%20didn't%20love%20the%20pay%2C%20but%20he%20was%20headed%20near%20where%20I%20lived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20got%20into%20my%20car%2C%20he%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20much%20did%20you%20get%20offered%20for%20this%20ride%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20told%20him%20it%20was%20about%20%247.50.%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20he%20was%20paying%20about%20%2428%20for%20the%20ride.%20He%20offered%20me%20%2420%20outside%20of%20the%20app%20to%20pick%20him%20up%20again%20later%2C%20but%20I%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20like%20somebody%20punched%20me%20in%20the%20chest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20a%20big%20shift%20for%20me.%20I%20was%20pissed%2C%20because%20not%20only%20was%20I%20getting%20less%20than%20half%20of%20the%20fare%2C%20I%20wasn't%20happy%20doing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI