s%20hesitant%2C%20but%20her%20perseverance%20convinced%20them.%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20in%20our%20community%20never%20went%20out%20without%20a%20veil%2C%20and%20I%20had%20never%20travelled%20even%20to%20the%20nearest%20urban%20area%20alone.%20As%20I%20departed%2C%20the%20entire%20village%20gathered%2C%20teary-eyed.%20No%20woman%20had%20ever%20set%20out%20alone%20on%20such%20a%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20trip%20to%20Kishangarh%2C%20marked%20by%20her%20first%20train%20ride%2C%20was%20both%20thrilling%20and%20intimidating.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20an%20entirely%20new%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20I%20felt%20the%20journey%20was%20endless%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fempbindi-international-4-1745562418.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fempbindi-international-4-1745562418.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fempbindi-international-4-1745562418-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fempbindi-international-4-1745562418-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fempbindi-international-4-1745562418-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fempbindi-international-4-1745562418-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-422894%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThavri%20received%20the%20Adi%20Sewa%20Gaurav%20Samman%20award%20and%20the%20Tribal%20Talent%20Award%20for%20her%20contributions.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuided%20by%20her%20trainers%2C%20